50
00:02:27,999 --> 00:02:29,292
No, you're too kind.

51
00:02:29,292 --> 00:02:30,918
You can't compare that Da Wu with that superstar.

52
00:02:30,918 --> 00:02:32,751
Luckily, I wasn't late.

53
00:02:32,751 --> 00:02:33,918
No, you're just in time.

54
00:02:33,918 --> 00:02:34,918
We saved a seat for you.

55
00:02:34,918 --> 00:02:36,799
Thank you.

56
