73
00:03:53,375 --> 00:03:55,542
I'll do it. Aren't you in a rush?

74
00:03:55,542 --> 00:03:57,584
Are you sure?

75
00:03:57,584 --> 00:04:00,032
Do I look unsure?

76
00:04:00,032 --> 00:04:02,646
You step on the gas pedal and I'll push from behind.

77
00:04:02,646 --> 00:04:03,883
Okay.

78
00:04:04,667 --> 00:04:06,042
But it's really deep.

79
00:04:06,042 --> 00:04:07,459
I'm not even sure myself.

80
00:04:07,459 --> 00:04:09,384
I'm certain.

81
00:04:10,000 --> 00:04:11,375
I guess so.

82
00:04:11,375 --> 00:04:13,334
Good morning, everyone.

83
00:04:13,334 --> 00:04:14,999
Good morning.

84
00:04:14,999 --> 00:04:16,667
For today's medical seminar,

85
00:04:16,667 --> 00:04:18,999
we have invited Dr. Chen Da Wu as our speaker.

86
00:04:18,999 --> 00:04:21,334
Dr. Chen was born in Kinmen.

87
00:04:21,334 --> 00:04:23,999
He went to elementary and middle school here.

88
00:04:23,999 --> 00:04:27,250
After graduating at 18, he went to study in Taipei

89
00:04:27,250 --> 00:04:29,542
and then furthered his studies in Canada.

90
00:04:29,542 --> 00:04:32,549
He specialized in family medicine,

91
00:04:32,549 --> 00:04:37,334
preventive medicine, geriatrics, and long-term care.

92
00:04:37,334 --> 00:04:40,542
This year, he made a very important decision.

93
00:04:40,542 --> 00:04:44,799
He decided to return to Kinmen to serve its people.

94
00:04:46,292 --> 00:04:50,626
So, today, we've specially invited Dr. Chen

95
00:04:50,626 --> 00:04:53,834
to share his work as a family physician.

96
00:04:53,834 --> 00:04:56,606
Let's give a warm round of applause

97
00:04:56,606 --> 00:04:59,050
to welcome Dr. Chen Da Wu!

98
00:05:06,231 --> 00:05:08,164
Hello, everyone.

99
00:05:08,164 --> 00:05:09,281
It has been a long time

100
00:05:09,281 --> 00:05:11,731
since I've seen so many friends and family together.

101
00:05:11,731 --> 00:05:13,167
First of all, I'd like to thank everyone

102
00:05:13,167 --> 00:05:16,339
for coming to my medical seminar.

103
00:05:16,339 --> 00:05:18,799
My name is Chen Da Wu. Nice to meet everyone.

104
00:05:20,459 --> 00:05:21,584
That's my son.

105
00:05:21,584 --> 00:05:23,740
I gave birth to him.

106
00:05:23,740 --> 00:05:27,782
My middle name, "Da," means "great."

107
00:05:27,782 --> 00:05:30,431
It represents my parents' expectations of me.

108
00:05:30,431 --> 00:05:33,083
They want me to be generous and courageous.

109
00:05:33,083 --> 00:05:36,431
However, I was a bit rebellious.

110
00:05:36,431 --> 00:05:39,263
I didn't want to just be a famous doctor,

111
00:05:39,263 --> 00:05:42,041
but a family physician who cares for people.

112
00:05:42,041 --> 00:05:44,422
Anyone who comes to see me,

113
00:05:44,422 --> 00:05:46,573
I won't see them as just a patient,

114
00:05:46,573 --> 00:05:51,424
but as a person with a name, a life, and a story.

115
00:05:51,424 --> 00:05:54,467
That's why I wanted to become a family physician.

116
00:06:00,514 --> 00:06:04,263
Next, I'd like to share my medical experiences overseas.

117
00:06:04,263 --> 00:06:06,050
- I'm stepping on it.
- Okay.

118
00:06:10,756 --> 00:06:12,973
Stop.

119
00:06:12,973 --> 00:06:14,799
