122
00:06:19,438 --> 00:06:21,467
Okay, I'll try.

123
00:06:22,380 --> 00:06:24,131
All right. One more time.

124
00:06:24,131 --> 00:06:26,365
Okay.

125
00:06:26,365 --> 00:06:28,209
One, two, three.

126
00:06:28,209 --> 00:06:30,164
One, two, three. Push!

127
00:06:30,164 --> 00:06:31,966
One more time.

128
00:06:31,966 --> 00:06:33,467
One, two, three.

129
00:06:34,966 --> 00:06:37,098
One more time.

130
00:06:37,098 --> 00:06:39,676
Okay, one, two, three.

131
00:06:43,834 --> 00:06:47,131
Almost there. Keep going. Come on.

132
00:06:47,131 --> 00:06:49,799
- All right. One, two, three.
- One, two, three.

133
00:06:50,999 --> 00:06:52,842
Keep going. Come on.

134
00:06:56,664 --> 00:06:58,679
Is that okay?

135
00:06:58,679 --> 00:06:59,909
One more time.

136
00:06:59,909 --> 00:07:01,799
One, two, three, push!

137
00:07:03,413 --> 00:07:05,372
It's moving.

138
00:07:05,372 --> 00:07:07,134
One, two, three. Push!

139
00:07:08,662 --> 00:07:10,587
Almost there!

140
00:07:11,734 --> 00:07:14,359
Come on. Keep going.

141
00:07:14,359 --> 00:07:15,525
Did you lift the tires?

142
00:07:15,525 --> 00:07:16,859
Yes.

143
00:07:16,859 --> 00:07:19,399
One more time. It's almost there!

144
00:07:19,399 --> 00:07:22,692
In the future, whenever you feel unwell,

145
00:07:22,692 --> 00:07:25,366
please feel free to consult your family physician.

146
00:07:25,366 --> 00:07:27,525
Anytime, anywhere.

147
00:07:27,525 --> 00:07:30,036
If there's anything I can help with,

148
00:07:30,036 --> 00:07:32,525
I'll always be here.

149
00:07:32,525 --> 00:07:34,199
Thank you.

150
00:07:35,913 --> 00:07:37,845
Gosh, that was fantastic.

151
00:07:37,845 --> 00:07:41,751
Thank you, Dr. Chen Da Wu for the wonderful talk.

152
00:07:41,751 --> 00:07:43,409
Great!

153
00:07:47,609 --> 00:07:49,333
Thank you.

154
00:07:49,333 --> 00:07:52,823
- Can we take a photo?
- Sure, come on.

155
00:07:52,847 --> 00:07:55,102
- Can we take a photo?
- Thank you very much.

156
00:07:55,102 --> 00:07:56,569
Thank you.

157
00:07:56,569 --> 00:07:57,810
I think you spoke better than me.

158
00:07:57,810 --> 00:07:59,652
No, you're the better speaker.

159
00:07:59,652 --> 00:08:01,234
Thank you, everyone.

160
00:08:01,234 --> 00:08:02,478
I'm really happy you could come today.

161
00:08:02,478 --> 00:08:04,276
- Thank you.
- Let me help you.

162
00:08:04,276 --> 00:08:05,609
- Yes, I'm glad you came today.
- Come on.

163
00:08:05,609 --> 00:08:07,012
- We'll stand here.
- Let me help you.

164
00:08:07,012 --> 00:08:09,483
Ready. One, two, three.

165
00:08:09,483 --> 00:08:11,826
All right. Let's take a look.

166
00:08:13,760 --> 00:08:16,534
All right. One, two, three.

167
00:08:16,534 --> 00:08:17,525
Yes.

168
00:08:17,525 --> 00:08:18,567
It's moving forward.

169
00:08:18,567 --> 00:08:20,199
Go.

